oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Performance - Bobby Hebb - 2006-07-21
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Performance by Bobby Hebb from the Ford Theater at the Country Music Hall of Fame and Museum on July 21, 2006. In support of the exhibit Night Train to Nashville: Music City Rhythm & Blues, 1945-1970. Hebb accompanies himself on guitar and piano.
